### 1. Get all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get all brands
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/brand
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get products by brand name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/brand/{{brandName}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get products by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/category/{{categoryName}}
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

### 6. Create a new product (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products/admin/createProduct
Cookie: accessToken={{jwtToken}}; token={{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "modelName": "Air Max 270",
